node.text: @starbucks has the most delicious assortment of cakes & beverages in Singapore, love their matcha latte, did some errands today during the circuit breaker, had to grab a matcha latte & almond croissant from them today, quite worth it 😊 Do you guys go out for beverages & a pastry @starbucks these days? Relaxing right now & missing these good times of going out comfortably. Stay safe & blessed my dear friends 💜 #starbuckssingapore #cakes #beverages #circuitbreakersg
